        <div class="container">
          <h2 class="section-title">Quick Start</h2>
          <div class="quickstart-steps">
            <div class="qs-step">
              <div class="qs-num">1</div>
              <p>Place <code>PxIgnis.jar</code> in your Fabric server's <code>mods/</code> folder.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="qs-step">
              <div class="qs-num">2</div>
              <p>Write scripts in <code>config/pxignis/scripts/</code>. The runtime loads all <code>*.lua</code> files alphabetically.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="qs-step">
              <div class="qs-num">3</div>
              <p>Run <code>/pxignis reload</code> in-game — no restart. Global data (<code>mc.data</code>) and per-player data auto-persist to JSON.</p>
            </div>
